# SPEC-SEC-001 REQ-SEC-010 — semgrep exclusion patterns.
#
# Scanned rule sets (configured in .github/workflows/security.yml):
#   p/golang, p/owasp-top-ten, p/jwt
#
# Excludes mirror .gosec.yml: tests and fixtures use intentionally-unsafe
# patterns that must not block the security gate. Findings outside these
# patterns are NEW findings and block the merge.

# Go test files and fixtures.
*_test.go
**/testdata/**

# Python sidecar test suites.
services/*/tests/**

# Frontend (covered by eslint + pnpm audit, not semgrep Go rules).
web/node_modules/**
web/.next/**

# Vendored / generated.
vendor/**
**/*_generated.go
**/*.pb.go

# Project metadata and docs (no executable code).
.moai/**
ops/security/**
docs/**
